audio_descriptions.notes:
The video opens with a scene of a woman standing in a dark forest with glowing human/fish hybrid creatures flying around her. It switches to a scene of a boy reading a book and looking at pictures of monsters on it's pages. 
The next two scenes are videos of large monsters in the water.
The scene shows video of a large tentacle coming out of the water and picking up a man standing next to the water.
The scene changes to a video of a street taken from several stories high, with three people running down the street.
The street scene replays. As the people run down the street a  3-story black gorilla, chases them and jumps on top of buildings. 
The scene changes to a street view from a surveillance camera showing people running and the gorilla chasing them down the street.
This scene shows a car sitting in the foreground and a dinosaur moving around behind it.  There is another dinosaur laying on the ground at its feet.
The scene shows video being taken as someone walks through an empty building with graffiti on the walls. A man is walking in front of the camera taking pictures.
There is a picture of a hallway with a blurry figure at the end, which looks somewhat like a lion.
The video shows what appears to be a naked person walking on all fours, and with hair like a lion's mane, coming through a doorway.  The camera person turns and runs away.
The scene shows video of a small town street on a foggy day.  Flashes of light in the background reveal the sillouette of a lizard-like form in the fog, looming over the tops of the buildings.
The scene shows a girl under bed covers screaming.
The video cuts to a scene from a movie where a woman is tied up in front of a large sea monster rising out of the water.
